ÃPeter & Muriel Kenny
We wrote your name In the sand, but the waves washed it away
We wrote your name in the sky, but the clouds blew it away
So we wrote your name in our hearts and forever it will stay"‘
—To our baby girl
OLIVIA "GASINETTICA" LANDRIAU SARACENT
Who was born sleeping on the 19th of June 2016 at 2.08am
"Out beyond ideas of right and wrong, there is a field
We will meet you there."
Mami & Papa"€
